name: powder
description:
POWDER is one of my first creative photography projects I worked on when venturing into the the studio / fashion industry 10 years ago. All images where captured in real life with no special fx at all. Just a great team, a massive mess with all the chocolate powder and flour.

The main photo with the chocolate powder I won a series of awards with over the year including second place in the ''Split Second" category at the Sony World Photography Awards and multiple awards in Ireland.
